# Fetch Pattern Required

- For any task involving data fetching, metadata generation, ISR/revalidate behavior, API endpoints, or server-side composition:
  - Read `.agents/skills/fetch-pattern/SKILL.md` before making changes.
  - Follow these conventions for shared fetch helpers, caching, `Promise.all`, and metadata mapping.
- Keep fetch logic server-first unless interactivity requires client-side fetching.
- Prefer consistent return shapes and typed responses.
